<br>
Wizards greater than lvl 10 (or 12, faulty memory) get an innate 2% chance for critical blasts.  The Spell Casting Fury (available to all casters, SFAIK) and Spell Casting Fury Mastery (Wizard-only) grant progressively higher chances of scoring critical blasts (and for more damage). <p><CENTER>
