<br>
you still get the effect of the fucus, but the effect is not critted.<br>
<br>
for example:<br>
<br>
if you have a nuke that does 1000 dmg and you wear focus, you do 1200.<br>
<br>
if you have crit3, you do not do a max of 2400.  instead the unfocused dmg is doubled (2000), then the focus effect (200) is added.  so you crit for 2200 max. <p><IMG SRC="http://becoop.brinkster.net/images/funnypics/ahrekb.jpg" usemap="#ahrekb" border="0">
